channel.title: Webclient - Downloads cache fine but does not extract?
channel.description:
Hey, Ive followed all the webclient tutorials and every single one brings me to this error:
Connection error - Retrying in 5 seconds.....
Ok so I looked into it and I relized that the cache.zip gets downloaded fine (Thank you fileden free hosting is ftw) but it never gets to "unpack" the zip.
Yet if I were to do it manually by going into my C:/SERVER.CACHE/cache.zip and extract it in the same folder, the webclient works fine.
So in conlcusion I have no Idea why it wont unpack. I have blurrr.java and gui.java that are untouched throughout every tutorial which could mabye be a problem. If anyone knows the answer and is willing to help me out... ~ Smitty
TY
